{"tid":113774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓航負債比逾10倍　韓元貶值「雪上加霜」","createTime":"2017-02-09T08:57:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T11:51:26.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fe877bab81539ce39b11ec655da07d6edeafbfc7","tid":113774,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T08:57:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/528/d528649.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F528%2Fd528649.jpg&h=09187b19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲分析師預估，大韓航空（KOREAN AIR）負債股權比即將超過1000%。（圖／資料照）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n財經中心／綜合報導<br />\n據《彭博》報導，大韓航空（KOREAN AIR）去年調降債信評等，負債股權比即將超過1000%，成為全服務航空公司（Full Service Carrier）裡負債最嚴重的航空公司。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">韓元持續貶值，今年甚至預估再貶7%，對於債比率較高的航空業來說，無異加重外債壓力</span>，而大韓航空公司的外幣債務將高過70%，此外韓亞航空（ASIANA AIRLINE）也佔一半多。<br />\n據了解，截至去年9月底，大韓航空負債股權比已達917%，因此穆迪投資者服務公司（Moody's Investors Service）的南韓辦事處（Korea Investors Service）預估第四季將突破1000%，韓亞航空與大韓航空今年恐面臨再度調降信評。<br />\n南韓穆迪投資者辦事處的分析師金楨勳（Kim Jung-hoon）認為，「今年經營環境可能變得更不有利，航空公司會發現更難減輕債務負擔，將會預見更多調降信評的理由。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 韓航負債比逾10倍　韓元貶值「雪上加霜」 | ETtoday財經新聞 | ETtoday 新聞雲 <a href=\"http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170208/862608.htm#ixzz4YB1fxr67\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20170208%2F862608.htm%23ixzz4YB1fxr67&d=piXtWL8Gd%2FER6BG70pbW9wHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=5f470880\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170208/862608.htm#ixzz4YB1fxr67</a><br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook"},{"pid":"c38310330c3b72c22d38b3ad9e45f5024fe69c26","tid":113774,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T08:58:32.000Z","msg":"KR 啲嘢算係好食<br />\n除此以外無咩好感 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0e5c46bce1bd4433712c85c3396334c1b4a9de","tid":113774,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T08:59:32.000Z","msg":"又一証明<br />\n邊個痴支那衰邊個"},{"pid":"af6f2a4cb9a4b75343bad67526941be3f4c64803","tid":113774,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T11:31:25.000Z","msg":"泡爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852ee640b62acb11b84a1e16c2f7c77113807652","tid":113774,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T11:40:07.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e1ca217ceaa304f0de038794d0dda702c7d7819","tid":113774,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T11:51:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}